cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.IR, cs.CY, cs.SD

This paper deals with analyzing news articles, which involves natural language processing and sentiment analysis. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses crowdsourcing to collect data, which falls under the sub-category of cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). The paper also compares articles across different news sources, which involves information retrieval and search engines, falling under the sub-category of cs.IR (Information Retrieval). The paper also deals with controversial issues, which can be related to cybersecurity (cs.CY) and social dynamics (cs.SD).
